two types of inventory
default inventory---------> /etc/ansible/hosts
inventory in users------------> /home/ozone/ansible/hosts


ansible all --list-hosts
[damu@localhost ansible]$ ansible all --list-hosts
  hosts (1):
    192.168.15.129
[damu@localhost ansible]$ 
172.16.15.127

go to vim /etc/hosts -----------> define ips
eg:
192.168.15.130 grey
192.168.15.129 blue
and then go to vim /etc/ansible/hosts
eg:
#vms
grey

